tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE player_interactions (    player_id INT,    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP,    in_game_chat_message TEXT );

CREATE TABLE sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT NOT NULL,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (player_id) REFERENCES players(player_id)
);

CREATE TABLE in_game_events (
    event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id INT,
    event_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    event_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    event_description TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES sessions(session_id)
);

CREATE TABLE chat_messages (
    message_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id INT,
    message_text TEXT,
    sender_id INT,
    receiver_id INT,
    message_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES sessions(session_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (sender_id) REFERENCES players(player_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (receiver_id) REFERENCES players(player_id)
);

CREATE TABLE user_behavior_analysis (
    behavior_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT,
    analysis_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    analysis_result TEXT,
    analysis_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (player_id) REFERENCES players(player_id)
);
